013public class ProductProjectionsSuggestGraphQLQuery extends GraphQLQuery {

016    super("query", queryName);
017    if (searchKeywords != null || fieldsSet.contains("searchKeywords")) {
018        getInput().put("searchKeywords", searchKeywords);
019    }if (fuzzy != null || fieldsSet.contains("fuzzy")) {
020        getInput().put("fuzzy", fuzzy);
021    }if (limit != null || fieldsSet.contains("limit")) {
022        getInput().put("limit", limit);
023    }if (staged != null || fieldsSet.contains("staged")) {

026  }
